(La)TeX font errors cheat sheet
===============================

Ever bumped into cryptic error messages when installing a font in (La)TeX?
Then this cheat sheet is for you.

It outlines (La)TeX's way of incorporating the font along the compilation
process, highlights what can go wrong along the process, and how (La)TeX
will complain about it. Some suggestions are made to remedy the situation
as well.

